Bennett Eli Rappaport (born March 23, 1986) is an American actor who plays Oliver "Ollie" Parker in the American TV series Mr. Robot. He played the role of Todd Dempsy in the NBC sitcom Outsourced, which aired during the 2010–11 television season. The series marked Rappaport's debut acting role on screen.
